uld be deduced that the enhanced wake prediction is predominantly due\nto the extra diffusion introduced by the CFD-driven model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 03:40:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 14:46:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-27"}
