rizontal shear and angle of internal friction with respect\nto particle size is also influenced by normal stress. Experimental results have\ngood agreement with the theoretical approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 03:49:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-22"}
