l chemistry and a set of\nproperties attractive for potential applications, but also demonstrated a\nfeasibility of surmounting conceptions common in material sciences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 13:13:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-06"}
