ng ordinary shock discontinuity. 2-D vortex preservation and double Mach\nreflection are tested on uniformed and randomized grids. The accomplishment by\nproposed schemes manifests their capability and robustness on solving problems\nunder rigorous circumstances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 00:58:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 03:10:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-26"}
